Preussag , Voest in joint venture . Germany ' s Preussag AG said on Tuesday that its steel unit Preussag Stahl AG and Voest - Alpine AG of Austria had agreed to form a joint venture to produce laser - welded plates for car manufacturers . The deal encompasses development , production and marketing of the plates and each partner will own equal shares of the new venture , which will involve new investment of around 35 million marks . - - Bonn newsroom , 49 228 26097 150 
